text: Sergei Aleksandrovich Filippov (; born 29 January 1967) is a former Russian football player. ==Club career== He made his Russian Premier League debut for FC Rostselmash Rostov-on-Don on 29 March 1992 in a game against FC Shinnik Yaroslavl.
